好多香港人都有20K/month</blockquote><br />\n睇佢衰樣都係假結婚過去</blockquote><br />\n美國以前大把假結婚<br />\n加拿大點會冇份<br />\n華人賤剷咁撚狡猾"},{"pid":"4ed4eb9a7e27dcfc44004c8ed7f162e1c7117a6a","tid":106560,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f472bc1454d2d6434a0c839470f0aa9ee03562a","tid":106560,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年收入4萬加幣即係月入2萬港幣，連20K/month都冇，好多香港人都有20K/month</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n楓國啲低技術工種(執貨，flip burger .etc) 既月薪扣埋稅大慨都係得三千多啲<br />\n姐係條友打既工唔會高級過呢啲工種<br />\n比著我係楓國政府都唔會要呢啲移民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做勞動工種就實要<br />\n但會留畀黑鬼做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4c7ba02cff9bbd1180ecafe83047ab22b47775","tid":106560,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年收入4萬加幣即係月入2萬港幣，連20K/month都冇，好多香港人都有20K/month</blockquote><br />\n睇佢衰樣都係假結婚過去</blockquote><br />\n美國以前大把假結婚<br />\n加拿大點會冇份<br />\n華人賤剷咁撚狡猾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比著你係正常虫國人<br />\n知道大陸煉獄咁既環境<br />\n仲唔快啲走啊？<br />\n<br />\n不過華人不嬲都係賤種<br />\n賤不在DNA<br />\n賤在文化教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4f554f22711951ee19e1c1d9e748b801b22960","tid":106560,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:47:53.000Z","msg":"支那愛國撚出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512e008e7f3008dfba53174a89cd2272359ca600","tid":106560,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"